{"tid":1803073,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"深水埗「黃店」摩登廚房遭爆竊　失兩日營業額共三萬元","createTime":"2019-12-30T02:46:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T07:42:30.000Z","uid":184822,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9d38806f492e26e16c143affa93b83d0c7797f42","tid":1803073,"uid":184822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T02:46:14.000Z","msg":"［紅媒01］今早（30日）6時半，深水埗黄竹街3號地舖一間餐廳遭爆竊，門鎖被撬開，警方接報後到場調查，而涉事的「摩登廚房」則早上暫停營業。老闆楊先生表示，翻看閉路電視片段，看見兩名中國籍賊人，戴有口罩﹑手套及風褸，事發時為凌晨二時多，賊人先於店外剪鎖，一小時後再折返爆竊，一人負責於店外看守，另一人則進店內爆竊。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家準備好罰佢哋未？</span></span>"},{"pid":"596a63e6177f07447b8ddd9b95dcd409d5eeb553","tid":1803073,"uid":200135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T02:59:59.000Z","msg":"深水埗黃竹街3號地下"},{"pid":"e8bd5f5fd3553c289a5f5711562dca7ff3d8047e","tid":1803073,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:03:13.000Z","msg":"根本唔應該keep咁多錢係公司,或者鎖入大夾萬"},{"pid":"4c3a6ca1190ad1b327ead040befc4a2fc1cad802","tid":1803073,"uid":7818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8bd5f5fd3553c289a5f5711562dca7ff3d8047e","tid":1803073,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:03:13.000Z","msg":"根本唔應該keep咁多錢係公司,或者鎖入大夾萬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:05:19.000Z","msg":"好難咁講<br />\n又要預錢找續<br />\n又要留錢找數<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留2-3日錢都正常"},{"pid":"f9ce2b2f77a3385ca052de4caa8e44ac13ea84d9","tid":1803073,"uid":63838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:07:20.000Z","msg":"對家就係用呢招打壓黃色經濟圈，順便比黑警賺下外快"},{"pid":"5918519a18ed4897f79e5bbf0fea2b2e925c67a7","tid":1803073,"uid":274435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8bd5f5fd3553c289a5f5711562dca7ff3d8047e","tid":1803073,"uid":196751,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-